The Care for Cancer Foundation is appealing to members of the public to donate towards their sanitary pack drive. Each pack is R100 and includes bath soap, bath sponge, tooth brush, toothpaste, lotion, powder, Dettol, toilet paper, tissue pack, ear buds, face cloth and cotton wool. The packs will be distributed to Hospices and Cancer Care Centres in and around KZN. If you would like more information or would like to donate, please call 031 836 8302. For more information you can visit their website www.careforcancer.org.za